{"date":"2007-01-30","platform":"OVA","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/14/29/56665_f0sX6.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/14/29/56665_f0sX6.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/14/29/56665_f0sX6.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/14/29/56665_f0sX6.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/14/29/56665_f0sX6.jpg"},"summary":"那是往返于记忆与思念之间的梦幻之旅。 \r\n少年沿着平日的归路，遇到着艳红和服，肩驻绿色小鸟的谜样少女，为其失魂落魄。然而少女只用绿色的羽，许下再见的约，便再无踪影。那之后50年，少年早已成年，不再记得少女的事情，偶然回到故乡。然而那少女，却还是少女的模样，出现在眼前。不知为 何自己也变回少年的样子，两人一起，从一间斗室，进入了七色幻想世界的旅行。这是过去还是现在？这是梦境还是现实？玻璃杯中漂浮着不可思议的七彩光谱，它又代表着什么？怀抱着种种疑问，少年意识到，少女和小鸟在向自己传达着什么…… ","name":"鳥の歌","name_cn":"鸟之歌","tags":[{"name":"OVA","count":90,"total_cont":0},{"name":"天野喜孝","count":76,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2007","count":65,"total_cont":0},{"name":"短片","count":58,"total_cont":0},{"name":"原创","count":33,"total_cont":0},{"name":"高梨康治","count":27,"total_cont":0},{"name":"东映","count":26,"total_cont":0},{"name":"東映アニメーション","count":19,"total_cont":0},{"name":"皆口裕子","count":10,"total_cont":0},{"name":"松原大典","count":10,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画短片","count":9,"total_cont":0},{"name":"东映动画","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"奇幻","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"独立ova","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本动画","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"00年代","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2007年","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"和风","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"乡里大辅","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2011-","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"个人喜好","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"水彩","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Short","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"SHORTS","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2004-06アニメ","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"爱情","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2007年1月","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"彩铅","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"神作","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"鸟之歌"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"v":"